revision.text:
'''Adam de Rodebroke''' was a Priest in the [[Roman Catholic Church]].

==Career==
Was presented the post of Vicar of [[St. Mary the Virgin, Aylesbury]] in December 1312 by [[Richard de Havering(priest)|Richard de Havering]], [[Prebendaries of Aylesbury|Prebendary of Aylesbury]]. He eventually resigned from the post.

